This jenkins
Install and configure Jenkins

Step 1 : Download Jenkins war file - https://jenkins.io/ 
Step 2 : Place the war file into any location on your system  (/opt)
Step 3 : goto folder where jenkins.war is  and run java -jar jenkins.war 
Step 4 : goto browser - http://localhost:8080  
Step 5 : install required plugins 
Step 6 : get started with Jenkins 

